snippet.title: Voice acting!
snippet.description:
Very happy with how the voice acting turned out. Big thanks to Asaki Yumemi (https://twitter.com/yumemi_0968) for providing the wonderful voice work! Check out her channel here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCF2kPljlZ-KhWyDPiJc6UDA
Game is on itch at https://tomboydrive.itch.io/tomboyadventure
